DesktopGroupId.description: The DesktopGroup Id  machine cost savings summary aggregation results are associated with.

SummaryDate.description: The SummaryDate of the machine cost savings summary. Machine Cost Saving Summary results are generated at hour, day and month level. Starting hour at 00:00:00.000 UTC

Granularity.description: The aggraegation Granularity of the generated machine cost savings summary per DesktopGroup. See enum [CostSavingsSummaryGranularity](/en-us/monitor-service-odata-api/monitor-service-enums#CostSavingsSummaryGranularity) for possible values.

HypervisorType.description: Column that denotes the HypervisorType of the machine that is associated with the aggregation results. See enum [HypervisorType](/en-us/monitor-service-odata-api/monitor-service-enums#HypervisorType) for possible values.

TagId.description: Autoscale TagId that is associated with the cost saving summary.

TotalMachinesCount.description: Column to hold the total machines count for the give DesktopGroupId of the machine cost savings summary.

PowerManagedMachinesOff.description: Total no of power managed machines that are in Off state for the given summary window.

PowerManagedMachinesInHibernate.description: Total no of power managed machines that are in Hibernate/Suspended state for the given summary window.

PowerManagedMachinesOnWithSessions.description: Total no of power managed machines that are in On state and have active sessions for the given summary window.

PowerManagedMachinesOnWithoutSessions.description: Total no of power managed machines that are in On state and without any active session for the given summary window.

PowerManagedMachineMinutesTurnedOff.description: Total cumulative Off minutes across all the power managed machines for the given desktop group for a given summary window.

TotalScaleInActions.description: Total no of scale in (power off) actions performed on the power managed machines during the summary window.

TotalHibernateActions.description: Total no of hibernate (suspend) actions performed on the power managed machines during the summary window.

TotalScaleOutActions.description: Total no of scale out (power on) actions performed on the power managed machines during the summary window.

TotalPeakConcurrentSessions.description: Total no of peak concurrent sessions running in the machines that part of a given desktop group for a given summary window.

AverageLogonDurationInSec.description: Value of average logon duration for sessions running in the machines across a give desktop group for a given summary window.

AveragePowerManagedMachinesCount.description: Average number of power managed machines part of a given desktop group for a given summary window.

AverageMachineCostPerHour.description: Per hour cost of a power managed machine for a given summary window. When the summary is done for granularity other than hour level, average cost is taken.

CostType.description: The cost type associate with the given desktop group level summary. See enum [CostType](/en-us/monitor-service-odata-api/monitor-service-enums#costtype) for possible values.

CurrencyType.description: The currency type associated with the given desktop group level summary. See enum [CurrencyType](/en-us/monitor-service-odata-api/monitor-service-enums#currencytype) for possible values.

TotalAmountSaved.description: Value calculated in a given summary window based on the machine poweroff minutes and cost saved for the machines across a given desktop group.

TotalCostIfNoPowerManagement.description: Total cost calculated if all the machines that are part of a given desktop group does not have power management capabilities.

TotalAutoscaleComputeSavings.description: Total amount saved in a given summary window on compute power due to the autoscale.

TotalAutoscaleStorageSavings.description: Total amount saved in a given summary window on storage due to the autoscale.

TotalEndUserComputeSavings.description: Total amount saved in a given summary window on compute power due to the end user actions on the machines for a given desktop group.

TotalEndUserStorageSavings.description: Total amount saved in a given summary window on storage due to the end user actions on the machines for a given desktop group.

AverageComputeCostPerHour.description: Average compute cost per hour for a given summary window.

AverageStorageCostPerHour.description: Average storage cost per hour for a given summary window.

TotalComputeCost.description: Total calculated compute cost based on the uptime for all the machines across a given desktop group for a given summary window.

TotalStorageCost.description: Total calculated storage cost based on the uptime for all the machines across a given desktop group for a given summary window.
